HEADWORD: Capsulotomy
<hw>Cap`su*lot"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Capsule</ets> + Gr. <?/ to cut.]</ety> <fld>(Surg.)</fld>
